data.description: Wonderful family home that is located in well known Oak Hills Park! This home features a grand den with cathedral ceilings, wood floors, wainscoting and cozy fireplace, updated spacious kitchen and large playroom for kids. This home has so many updates - NEW interior and exterior paint, New quartz countertops and tile backsplash in kitchen with basin sink, New quartz countertops in all bathrooms, New designer tile flooring in master bathroom, New carpet in all bedrooms, formal living and dining room, updated most interior light fixtures. Oversized Master bedroom with ensuite bath with double vanities. The backyard includes an amazing pool with a new pool filter, large yard with fresh landscaping and plenty of covered storage. New energy efficient R30 insulation and 70W solar-powered attic fan that reduces heat and moisture in attic at no cost to operate. PLANNED ROOF REPLACEMENT NOVEMBER 2023! Located near Perkins Rowe, on St. Jude Bus Route and Interstate. This home is move in ready!
